## Operator Breakdown
- **σ (Air/Aerunik — Distinction)**: safe|dangerous — The primary distinction in primal beliefs: whether the world is fundamentally safe or dangerous; Safe correlates with optimism at r=0.61
- **ρ (Water/Sentaria — Relation)**: enticing|dull — The relational dimension of world-engagement; Enticing world belief negatively correlates with depression at r=-0.52
- **λ (Fire/Jvalion — Transformation)**: perception|belief_shift — The Alive dimension animating transformation; world perceived as dynamic, intentional, responsive
- **β (Wood/Arboriel — Growth)**: optimism|flourishing — Growth outcomes predicted by primals; explains more variance in life satisfaction, trust, and gratitude than Big Five personality
- **δγ (Earth/Humavita — Cycling)**: test_retest|stability — Remarkable temporal stability: r=0.88 at 2 weeks, r=0.75 at 9 months, r=0.77 at 19 months
- **μ (Metal/Ferrosid — Structure)**: PI99|taxonomy — The PI-99 inventory structure: 26 primals organized into 3 higher-order categories with high internal consistency (alpha=0.93)

